Now taking Enrollment for Kindergarten and TK for the 2020-2021 school year.

Enrollment packets for Kindergarten and TK are available for pick up at the Kelso Cafeteria and at the food stops. When you have completed the Enrollment packet please return to these locations. You may turn in the rest of the documentation, copy of birth certificate, immunization record, school entry physical and dental health the 2 weeks before school starts. The first day of school is August 12, 2020.
